<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12043d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12043d">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12043d"> 43(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 12 nights&apos; wake</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">179-80: The news of the death of our great Saint soon spread through the length and breadth of the land <font color="green">[&ldquo;]</font> The funeral obsequies lasted for twelve whole days <font color="green">[&ldquo;]</font> For a space of twelve nights, that is, whilst the divines were waking him <font color="green">[&ldquo;]</font> there was no night, but angelic light <small> Very Rev. Dean Kinane, <a name="TKSP" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#TKSP"><cite title="source">St. Patrick: his life, his heroic virtues, his labours, and the fruits of his labours</cite></a>, (ed. unknown) 179-80</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
